description.narrative: Human resources (8 technical and 7 admin) managing the project .Each personnel is allocated a percentage of time . The project is managed by a Project Management Unit (PMU) located at the KHF Head Office managed by a project manager with the support of an M& E specialist, a media and communication specialist, procurement and logistic specialist with the support of a driver, and a finance manager . The PMU oversees the work of shadows in the implementing entities including, coordinators, M&E, communication and media, logistics and procurement as well as Finance personnel.
